fields.title: Ziabags Orbit - Set Of 3
fields.description: Move in Style with Skybags Orbit, an airline compliant hard luggage trolley with ample storage space to accommodate your belongings. This stylish yet sturdy trolley bag is available in a set of 3 and can be easily nested to save on storage space. It is equipped with dual wheels, TSA approved lock, anti theft zipper and a multi stage push button trolley to help you travel with ease.
fields.Specifications:
STYLISH AND STURDY: The Orbit trolley bag is designed to help you travel in style. This lightweight bag is made of durable and scratch resistant ABS material which makes it sturdy, waterproof and impact resistant. 
EASY TO MOVE: This trolley bag is equipped with smooth dual wheels and an adjustable trolley handle which make it easy to carry it on various surfaces.
ENHANCED SECURITY: The TSA approved lock and anti theft zipper ensure your belongings are safe while you embark on new adventures.
